I am very grateful that I'm humbly finished this course of Autodesk Certified Professional: Revit for  Architectural Design Exam Prep. I learned a lot and thank you so much for the step by step teaching video tools. Now I am ready to use the Revit BIM software for my Architectural drawing plans. My purpose to enroll this course is to enhance and familiarized my self regarding the used of Revit, which are now the most highly in demand software tools in Architectural and Construction industry.  I will highly recommend Autodesk Revit/BIM! Cheers and good luck!

I think the schedule for the course should be more stretched out if they want students to actually follow along with the videos and practice exercises.
